&lt;p&gt;Darkness in the whole existence is natural. &lt;br&gt;
It need not be created. &lt;br&gt;
Darkness is universal. &lt;br&gt;
But by effort if you can bring light  &lt;br&gt;
then darkness disappears!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where does it go?  &lt;br&gt;
Does it get contracted or Displaced? &lt;br&gt;
If you light all the places then  &lt;br&gt;
will there be lessor darkness  &lt;br&gt;
in the world because it has been displaced?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
